<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Castela</i> <i>emoryi</i> grows as individual shrubs or in stands with <i>Ambrosia</i> <i>dumosa</i>, <i>Brickellia</i> <i>incana</i>, <i>Encelia</i> <i>farinosa</i>, <i>Encelia</i> <i>virginensis</i> and <i>Larrea</i> <i>tridentata</i>. </div>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Shrubs < 4 m; canopy is open to intermittent. </div>
</div>

        
